                <head ana="#head_untitled-inferred-from-preceding-sibling-head">[Untitled]</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Extract.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1912-02-08">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 8, 1912</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Zenón Toribio was killed in an engagement with Government forces yesterday.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Russell</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
